{"id":"14ab2213-6d2a-4b88-a552-1600ecfa4e12","name":"Telemachus | EPIC The Musical","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>\"If you'd ever want to... I wouldn't be opposed to spending time together. In the gardens, I mean... When flowers are in bloom. The sight surely sets ones heart ablaze.\"</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">.⋅˚₊‧ 🜲 ‧₊˚⋅.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Sometimes a savage finds a way into the nobles home. And sometimes, the savage turns out to be just what the noble needed. Saving another isn't hard, but brushing off the praise after it takes a true saviour to speak.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">.⋅˚₊‧ 🜲 ‧₊˚⋅.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">_______________________________________</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Hello avians!</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">I have blessed you once again with a new story, and so fast too! Wow, so vigilant... lol</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">This time of the prince himself. I wanted to make it somewhat of a teen romance/friendship dynamic, so hopefully you'll have some fluff to write in these trying times where such topics are so hard to come by!</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">_______________________________________</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Epic The Musical Series Shortcuts:</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/c616d9ea-f00a-403d-9a15-9036133364e5_character-poseidon-epic-the-musical\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 127, 193);\"><strong>× Poseidon | One With Lost Treasure</strong></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/7e146bbe-3596-4f3c-9e60-2ca1a2a12caa_character-ares-epic-the-musical\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(179, 28, 28);\"><strong>× Ares | The Kin Of Wrath</strong></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noref